'''圣塔克拉·海马诺特教堂'''（{{lang-en|St. Takla Haymanot's Church}}）是[[埃及|埃及]][[亚历山大城|亚历山大城]]的[[科普特正教会|科普特正教会]]教堂。位于易卜拉欣区，靠近亚历山大体育俱乐部. 该堂在1969年6月19日祝圣，供奉13世纪埃塞俄比亚修士塔克拉·海马诺特。<ref name="History">{{Cite web |url=http://st-takla.org/Church-history-1.html |title=History of Saint Takla Himanout's Church |publisher=Official website of St. Takla Haymanot's Church |accessdate=2011-02-10 |archive-date=2019-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115070019/https://st-takla.org/Church-history-1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2007年7月15日，埃塞俄比亚牧首Abune Paulos为了修复[[埃塞俄比亚正教会|埃塞俄比亚正教会]]和[[亚历山大科普特正教会|亚历山大科普特正教会]]之间的关系，对埃及进行地标旅行期间，曾访问该堂<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://st-takla.org/Gallery/07-Pope-of-Ethiopia-Visit-to-St-TekleHimanot-Church/Abune-Paulos_Visit-15-07-2007_Coptic-Ethiopian-Relationship_01.html |title=H. H. Abune Paulos, Patriarch of Ethiopia: Visit to St. Teklehaimanot Church in Alexandria (July 15, 2007) |publisher=Official website of St. Takla Haymanot's Church |accessdate=2011-02-10 |archive-date=2011-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110119041707/http://st-takla.org/Gallery/07-Pope-of-Ethiopia-Visit-to-St-TekleHimanot-Church/Abune-Paulos_Visit-15-07-2007_Coptic-Ethiopian-Relationship_01.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该堂所有的圣像均为著名埃及艺术家Isaac Fanous的作品。<ref name="History"/> 该堂维护互联网上最好的科普特相关网站之一。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://st-takla.org/News/Best-Coptic-Sites-in-Egypt.html |title=Best Coptic Sites for 2004 |publisher=Official website of St. Takla Haymanot's Church |accessdate=2011-02-10 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207032542/https://st-takla.org/News/Best-Coptic-Sites-in-Egypt.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

